description: Crispy crumbed fish served with a tangy pineapple salsa.
keywords: Fish dishes,Pescatarian,Soy free,Tree nut free,Egg free,Pineapple,Peanut free
name: Crispy Fish With Pineapple Salsa Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 1 packet 425g Frozen Birds Eye Oven Bake Crumbed Fish Fillets - Original
1 cup fresh ripe pineapple, finely diced
0.25 red onion, peeled and finely chopped

recipeInstructions.text: Cook Birds Eye Oven Bake Fish Fillets following packet directions.
Combine remaining ingredients to make a salsa and serve with cooked fish.
